organic.title: Samaritan Evergreen Hospice
organic.snippet: Samaritan Evergreen Hospice supports patients, and their families, who live in Benton, Lincoln, Linn, Marion, Polk and parts of Tillamook counties.

organic.title: Hospice House - Samaritan Health Services
organic.snippet: Samaritan Evergreen Hospice House in Albany is an inpatient facility for patients who are near end of life.
